---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Molinello Music" description="The story behind Molinello Music, founded by Boyd Timothy.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-12 text-center">About</h1>

      <div class="md:flex gap-12 items-start mb-12">
        <div class="md:w-2/5 mb-8 md:mb-0 space-y-4">
          <img src="/images/about/boyd-cycling.jpg" alt="Boyd Timothy cycling in the mountains" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full" />
          <img src="/images/about/molinello-amps.jpg" alt="Molinello hand-built tube amplifiers" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full" />
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-3/5 space-y-6 text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Molinello Music began with a trip Boyd and his wife took to
            <a href="https://www.molinello.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">Il Molinello</a>,
            a small agriturismo in the rolling hills of Tuscany. They stayed long enough for the place to leave its mark&mdash;its history, warmth, and connection to the land. One of the owners was an avid cyclist, and Boyd (also a cyclist) connected with him immediately. The trip sparked a deep fascination with Italian culture and craftsmanship.
          </p>
          <p>
            When Boyd began creating things&mdash;custom bike jerseys, hand-built guitar tube amplifiers, and releasing music with his band&mdash;he needed a name that tied together music, bikes, good design, and the joy of building with care. "Molinello Music" felt like the right fit.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, Molinello Music is a creative home base: a small, personal brand dedicated to crafting high-quality musical gear and releasing original music. Everything is driven by curiosity, passion, and a love of making things that feel both useful and meaningful.
          </p>
          <p>Thanks for stopping by&mdash;and for being part of this ongoing adventure.</p>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark">Boyd Timothy</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
            *I have no affiliation with them, but it was an excellent place to vacation!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
